title: [2006] Forgive Durden - Wonderland
description:
Wonderland is the debut studio album of Forgive Durden. It was released by Fueled by Ramen on May 9, 2006. The album (or a majority of the songs on it) makes references to the works of Lewis Carroll, including Alice&#039;s Adventures In Wonderland, and Jabberwocky.
